lover 处理\n- Auth owner-only tools 权限修复\n- Gateway readiness probes 新功能\n- Compaction 可配置化\n- Container extensions build arg\n\n#### 🟢 低优先级更新 (36个)\n- CI/工具改进 (14个)\n- 依赖清理 (3个)\n- 文档更新 (5个)\n- 其他小修复\n\n### 📊 统计数据\n\n| 类型 | 数量 | 占比 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Bug 修复 | 22 | 44% |\n| 新功能 | 4 | 8% |\n| 安全修复 | 2 | 4% |\n| 依赖清理 | 3 | 6% |\n| CI/工具改进 | 14 | 28% |\n| 文档更新 | 5 | 10% |\n\n### 主要贡献者\n- Vincent Koc\n- Shadow\n- OfflynAI\n- SP\n- Marcus Widing\n- Anton Eicher\n- Wei Zhou\n- Altay\n- Efe Büken\n- Drew Wagner\n\n### 产出文件\n- `memory/openclaw-updates/update-2026-03-07.md` (7.5KB)\n- `memory/analyze-openclaw-fix-report-20260307-1030.md` (1.4KB)\n\n### 行动建议\n1. ⚠️ **立即更新**: 安全修复和关键 Bug 修复\n2. ✅ **本周更新**: Feishu、Venice、Gateway 相关更新\n3. 🟢 **可选更新**: CI 工具和文档更新\n\n### 升级命令\n```bash\ncd /root/openclaw-fork\ngit fetch upstream\ngit merge upstream/main\npnpm install && pnpm build\npnpm test\n# 重启服务\n```\n\n### 下次分析\n**时间**: 2026-03-14 (1 周后)\n**重点关注**:\n- Venice kimi-k2-5 模型稳定性\n- iMessage echo loop 修复反馈\n- Feishu timeout 修复验证"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1724,"output":1232,"cacheRead":28096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31052,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772850780895}}
