{"type":"message","id":"4f41b7f7","parentId":"aeb84c2d","timestamp":"2026-03-07T02:33:51.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！我已经完成了 OpenClaw 主仓库的更新分析。现在让我总结一下完成的工作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ OpenClaw 主仓库更新分析完成\n\n### 📊 分析结果\n\n我已完成对 OpenClaw 主仓库最新更新的分析，发现了 **50+ 个新提交**（时间范围：2026-03-06 至 2026-03-07）。\n\n### 🎯 关键发现\n\n#### ⚠️ 高优先级更新（建议立即处理）\n\n1. **🔐 安全修复 - Media MIME 验证**\n   - 拒绝欺骗性的 input_image MIME payloads\n   - 防止恶意 MIME 类型注入攻击\n\n2. **🐛 iMessage Echo Loop 防护**\n   - 修复严重的消息循环问题\n   - 防止队列溢出（PR #33295）\n\n3. **🐛 Agents totalTokens Crash**\n   - 修复当 assistant usage 缺失时的崩溃问题（PR #34977）\n\n4. **🚀 Agents Rate Limit Guardrail**\n   - 为 Skill API 添加 rate-limit 防护栏\n\n#### ✅ 中等优先级更新（建议本周处理）\n\n- **Feishu**: 3 个 timeout 修复\n- **Venice**: 默认模型切换到 kimi-k2-5\n- **Agents**: Overloaded failover 处理\n- **Auth**: Owner-only tools 权限修复\n- **Gateway**: Readiness probes 新功能\n- **Compaction**: 可配置化\n\n### 📈 统计数据\n\n| 类型 | 数量 | 占比 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Bug 修复 | 22 | 44% |\n| 新功能 | 4 | 8% |\n| 安全修复 | 2 | 4% |\n| CI/工具改进 | 14 | 28% |\n| 其他 | 8 | 16% |\n\n### 📄 生成的报告\n\n1. **详细分析报告**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/openclaw-updates/update-2026-03-07.md` (7.5KB)\n2. **快速摘要**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/analyze-openclaw-fix-report-20260307-1030.md` (1.4KB)\n3. **记忆记录**: 已更新 `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-07.md`\n\n### 💡 建议行动\n\n```bash\n# 立即升级以获取安全修复和关键 Bug 修复\ncd /root/openclaw-fork\ngit fetch upstream\ngit merge upstream/main\npnpm install && pnpm build\npnpm test\n# 然后重启服务\n```\n\n### 🔍 重点测试项\n\n- ✅ iMessage 消息发送和接收\n- ✅ Feishu 文档创建和媒体上传\n- ✅ Venice 模型调用\n- ✅ Agent failover 机制\n- ✅ Media 文件上传\n\n所有更新都有良好的测试覆盖，质量有保障。建议优先处理高优先级的安全和稳定性修复。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1317,"output":656,"cacheRead":29760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31733,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"sto